## 5. Administrative Workflow

Used by system administrators to maintain the application.

### **Flow Description:**
1.  **User Management**: Admin creates user accounts for new staff and assigns roles (e.g., Doctor, Nurse).
2.  **Role Management**: configuring what each role can see or do (Permissions).
3.  **Master Data**: Managing Departments, Wards, and other hospital constants.

### **Diagram**

```mermaid
graph LR
    Admin((Admin)) -->|Manage| Users[Users]
    Admin -->|Manage| Dept[Departments]
    Admin -->|Manage| Roles[Roles & Permissions]
    
    Roles -.->|Controls| Access[User Access Level]
```
